  "a":[
    {
      "e":"p",
      "s":[
        { "e":"span", "t":"此作品主要在於開發出可以在 Google Maps 上面編輯基本路徑的功能，利用 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps JavaScript API", "attr":{ "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/?hl=zh-tw", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 設計出規劃路線的工具，並且可以匯出路間經緯度 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Excel", "attr":{ "href":"https://products.office.com/zh-tw/excel", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":"。" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "e":"p",
      "s":[
        { "e":"span", "t":"在 Google Maps 上顯示選單，主要是使用 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps JavaScript Events", "attr":{ "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/events?hl=zh-tw", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 來實作，並且搭配 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Marker", "attr":{ "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/markers", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":"、" },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Polyline", "attr":{ "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/polyline-simple?hl=zh-tw", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 來繪製出路線圖，並且針對 Marker 綁定 Event 來實作 " },
        { "e":"b", "t":"刪除節點" },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 的功能。" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "e":"p",
      "s":[
        { "e":"span", "t":"此實作中有一項特別的技巧，就是在 Ployline 上點擊滑鼠右鍵時，必須要可以 插入節點 的功能，難點是在於 Maps 上的 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps Position", "attr":{ "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/control-positioning?hl=zh-tw", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 與 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps Point", "attr":{ "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/icon-complex", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 物件的" },
        { "e":"a", "t":"轉換", "attr":{ "href":"https://github.com/comdan66/OA-googleMapsMenu/blob/master/js/public.js#L51", "target":"_blank" } },
        { "e":"span", "t":"，必須將點擊位置的經緯度經計算後得知在地圖元素上相對應的 left、top 數值，再將選單顯示在該位置上。" }
      ]
    },
    { "e":"p", "t":"因為要針對不同區段的 Polyline 監聽 Event，所以必須使用特別的方式去畫出 Polyline，目前我所使用的方法是將 Markers 之間用單個 Polyline 做連接，所以地圖上 Polyline 的數量會是 Marker 的 n-1 個，如此一來就可以對每段 Polyline 監聽 Event 了！" },
    { "e":"p", "t":"當插入節點時，便可以取出該 Polyline 是位於哪兩個 Markers 之間，這時候再針對陣列去做橋接，重組後的 Markers 陣列再重新繪製一次 Polyline 即可！" }
